description: NEO Battery Materials Ltd., a junior resource company, focuses on the exploration of battery metals in North America. The company holds interests in various mining claims covering 467 hectares located in Golden, British Columbia. It also focuses on developing silicon anodes. The company was formerly known as Pan Andean Minerals Ltd. and changed its name to NEO Battery Materials Ltd. in March 2021. NEO Battery Materials Ltd. was incorporated in 2006 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
